      "rationale": "Code verification performed using method of manufactured solutions (MMS) for the incompressible Navier-Stokes solver. Observed order of accuracy (1.97) is consistent with theoretical second-order spatial accuracy. Benchmark comparisons against three ASME V&V 20 test cases passed. Gradation 3 achieved."
