      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/equivalency-inputs-mrl5-gradation2",
      "rationale": "CFD boundary conditions (inlet velocity profiles, rotational speed, fluid properties) mapped directly from bench test measurements. Equivalency verified via parameter comparison table documented in simulation plan. Minor discrepancy in fluid temperature (bench: 37±0.5°C; CFD: 37°C fixed) assessed as negligible via sensitivity run (NIH change < 0.8%). Gradation 2 achieved."
